## Node.js

An asynchronous event-driven JavaScript runtime we used to support a small footprint deployment process. Visit the [Official Node.js Documentation](https://nodejs.org/en/docs/) to learn more about Node.js, and check out our tutorials for [installing the Node.js Package Manager (NPM) on a Mac](/get-started/installing-nodejs-mac) or [Windows](/get-started/installing-nodejs-windows).
